I’m excited and blessed to announce that I have joined The Agency, Pacific Palisades office! I’m humbled to be able to work with such an amazing group of people that are the best in their industry. 

If you know me, you’d know that I’m BIG on real estate! It’s almost all I talk about at times. I look forward to suiting up with a new kind of team and turning this lifelong passion into a profession.

Today marks an exciting milestone as I introduce you to @shopenergize ⚡️ caffeinated gum! It’s been an incredible journey turning a concept into reality. This creation has been a huge learning experience, and I couldn’t be prouder of it. For just $11.99, you can grab a 3-pack of gum, and all it takes is a like, comment, and share to help spread the word. Your support means the world to me, and I can’t thank you enough for being part of this journey! 🙏 #EnergizeLaunch #EnergizeGum #FromConceptToReality
🎉 Celebrating 250 Energize Packs Sold! Big thanks to all of you for your amazing support. Get ready for the exciting chapters that lie ahead! ⚡️🔋 #EnergizeGum #MoreToCome
I’m not a businessman, I’m a business, man.

“I’m humble enough to eat crumbs off the right table.” Surrounding yourself with inspiring individuals who uplift and motivate is paramount. @proathletecommunity has provided the perfect environment for my journey, igniting the fire needed to turn dreams into reality. Returning to share my journey and transition has been an incredible experience. Huge appreciation to PAC for everything 🙌🏽📈

“Gods word is a lamp to my feet and a light for my path.” Psalms 119:105 🙏🏽 Thank you to @proathletecommunity for being that light and always thank you God for illuminating my path. I may not be able to see what’s in front of me, but you show me what steps to take and that’s all I need. You’ve never failed me.
